passages.text:
You return to the open air overlook.  The air surrounding the crib has somehow grown even more fetid.

Julia::Please, Miss.  I don't want to be here...

Jasper::Lingering here is painful and cancerous.

Jasper::But you need it; the psychic equivalent of cutting.

Jasper::Soak it in for just a bit.

[[p:Yeah, let's get out of here...]]
[[p:Ugh, alright.]]
